      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. The engine has significant issues, including a noticeable knock and heavy oil leaks, and the transmission slips when shifting into higher gears. The exterior has extensive rust on the rocker panels and wheel wells, along with multiple dents and fading paint. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with several tears, and most of the electronic features, including the radio and power windows, are non-functional. This car would be best suited as a parts donor or a major project for someone with mechanical expertise.",
