    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a major project or a source for parts. The exterior shows significant wear, including noticeable rust patches, several large dents, and fading clear coat across most panels. Mechanically, the engine requires a comprehensive overhaul to be reliable, and the transmission exhibits frequent slipping. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with several tears, and many of the electronic components, including the radio and power windows, are currently non-functional. It will likely need to be towed from its current location.",
