    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused BMW E46 M3. This example features the legendary S54B32 straight-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double VANOS variable valve timing. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers crisp engagement, paired with the factory M Variable Differential Lock for optimal power delivery out of corners. Recent preventative maintenance includes a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive valve clearance adjustment. The chassis remains taut with upgraded polyurethane bushings, ensuring the suspension geometry stays true under high lateral loads. While the exterior and interior show minor signs of honest use consistent with its age, the powertrain and drivetrain remain a sharp, high-revving precision instrument ready for the apex.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
